Cell["\<\
The above density matrix is expressed in terms of Ket[]**Bra[] forms. It can \
be expressed in terms of spin operators.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->476051865,ExpressionUUID->"49e433cd-f850-4ffd-a8f1-a7861240a284"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
